---
// Spectre Browser — landing page
// Built with Astro. Deploy to any static host.
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Spectre — Browse Without a Trace</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Spectre is a Firefox fork with tracking protection, fingerprint resistance, and zero telemetry — compiled in, not just configured." />

  <meta property="og:type"        content="website" />
  <meta property="og:url"         content="https://koels.site/spectre" />
  <meta property="og:title"       content="Spectre — Browse Without a Trace" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="A Firefox fork with strict tracking protection, fingerprint resistance, and zero telemetry — on by default, compiled in." />
  <meta property="og:image"       content="https://koels.site/og.png" />
  <meta property="og:image:width"  content="1200" />
  <meta property="og:image:height" content="630" />
  <meta property="og:site_name"   content="Spectre Browser" />
  <meta property="og:locale"      content="en_US" />

  <meta name="twitter:card"        content="summary_large_image" />
  <meta name="twitter:title"       content="Spectre — Browse Without a Trace" />
  <meta name="twitter:description" content="A Firefox fork with strict tracking protection, fingerprint resistance, and zero telemetry — on by default." />
  <meta name="twitter:image"       content="https://koels.site/og.png" />

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --bg:       #05050f;
      --bg2:      #08081a;
      --surface:  rgba(255,255,255,0.035);
      --surface2: rgba(255,255,255,0.065);
      --border:   rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      --border2:  rgba(255,255,255,0.13);
      --text:     #eeeeff;
      --muted:    rgba(238,238,255,0.52);
      --dim:      rgba(238,238,255,0.28);
      --cyan:     #00ccff;
      --cyan2:    #66deff;
      --violet:   #7b5fff;
      --green:    #00e87a;
      --red:      #ff4560;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      min-height: 100vh;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      position: relative;
    }

    /* subtle dot grid across whole page */
    body::before {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.028) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 28px 28px;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    /* everything above the grid */
    nav, main, footer, .stats-strip, .policy-section { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

    /* ─── NAV ─── */
    nav {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 0 2.5rem;
      height: 56px;
      background: rgba(5,5,15,0.82);
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .logo {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text);
      text-decoration: none;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.6rem;
    }

    .logo-dot {
      width: 7px;
      height: 7px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--cyan);
      box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--cyan), 0 0 16px rgba(0,204,255,0.4);
    }

    .nav-right {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1.75rem;
      list-style: none;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      color: var(--muted);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      transition: color 0.15s;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--text); }

    .nav-gh {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.4rem;
      padding: 0.38rem 0.9rem;
      border-radius: 6px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border2);
      background: var(--surface);
      color: var(--muted);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
    }

    .nav-gh:hover { border-color: var(--cyan); color: var(--text); }

    /* ─── HERO ─── */
    .hero {
      position: relative;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 9rem 1.5rem 7rem;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-glow {
      position: absolute;
      top: -80px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 1000px;
      height: 600px;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 35%,
        rgba(0,204,255,0.11) 0%,
        rgba(123,95,255,0.07) 40%,
        transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      padding: 0.28rem 0.9rem;
      border-radius: 99px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,204,255,0.22);
      background: rgba(0,204,255,0.06);
      color: var(--cyan2);
      font-size: 0.76rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      margin-bottom: 2.25rem;
    }

    .badge-pulse {
      width: 6px;
      height: 6px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--cyan);
      box-shadow: 0 0 6px var(--cyan);
      animation: blink 2.4s ease infinite;
    }

    @keyframes blink {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
      50% { opacity: 0.25; }
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.0;
      letter-spacing: -0.045em;
      max-width: 860px;
      margin-bottom: 1.6rem;
    }

    .hero h1 .line-ghost {
      display: block;
      color: transparent;
      -webkit-text-stroke: 1.5px rgba(238,238,255,0.18);
    }

    .hero h1 .line-solid {
      display: block;
    }

    .hero h1 .accent {
      background: linear-gradient(100deg, var(--cyan), var(--cyan2) 60%, #aaf0ff);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }

    .hero-sub {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 500px;
      line-height: 1.75;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    /* ─── DOWNLOAD ─── */
    .download-wrap {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.6rem;
      padding: 0.9rem 2.2rem;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #008ab5, #00ccff 80%);
      color: #010a0f;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      text-decoration: none;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
      box-shadow: 0 0 28px rgba(0,204,255,0.28), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      position: relative;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 40px rgba(0,204,255,0.42), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    }

    .btn-primary:active { transform: translateY(0); }

    .btn-primary.soon {
      background: var(--surface2);
      color: var(--muted);
      box-shadow: none;
      border: 1px solid var(--border2);
      cursor: not-allowed;
      opacity: 0.55;
    }

    .btn-primary.soon::after {
      content: 'builds in progress';
      position: absolute;
      top: -22px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      color: var(--cyan);
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .platform-row {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.55rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .btn-platform {
      padding: 0.38rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 6px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--dim);
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      cursor: not-allowed;
    }

    .platform-hint {
      font-size: 0.76rem;
      color: var(--dim);
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    }

    /* ─── STATS STRIP ─── */
    .stats-strip {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: var(--bg2);
      overflow-x: auto;
    }

    .stat {
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 160px;
      max-width: 260px;
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
      text-align: center;
      border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .stat:last-child { border-right: none; }

    .stat-value {
      display: block;
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    }

    .stat-value.c { color: var(--cyan); }
    .stat-value.g { color: var(--green); }

    .stat-label {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    }

    /* ─── FEATURES ─── */
    .section {
      padding: 6rem 1.5rem;
      max-width: 1080px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .section-tag {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--cyan);
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    }

    .section h2 {
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.035em;
      line-height: 1.1;
      margin-bottom: 2.75rem;
    }

    /* bento grid */
    .bento {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr);
      gap: 0.9rem;
    }

    .card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 1.6rem;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .card::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0; right: 0;
      width: 100px;
      height: 100px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(0,204,255,0.055), transparent 65%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .card:hover {
      border-color: rgba(0,204,255,0.22);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.055);
    }

    .c2 { grid-column: span 2; }
    .c3 { grid-column: span 3; }

    .card-icon {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
    }

    .card-title {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      margin-bottom: 0.45rem;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .card-body {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    .card-body code {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.82em;
      color: var(--cyan2);
      background: rgba(0,204,255,0.07);
      border-radius: 3px;
      padding: 0.1em 0.35em;
    }

    .card-chip {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 1rem;
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      color: var(--cyan);
      background: rgba(0,204,255,0.07);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,204,255,0.15);
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 0.18rem 0.5rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }

    /* ─── FORK NOTICE ─── */
    .fork-wrap {
      max-width: 1080px;
      margin: -2rem auto 4rem;
      padding: 0 1.5rem;
    }

    .fork-inner {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      align-items: flex-start;
      padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: rgba(123,95,255,0.05);
      border: 1px solid rgba(123,95,255,0.18);
    }

    .fork-inner p {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    .fork-inner strong { color: var(--text); }

    /* ─── PRIVACY POLICY ─── */
    .policy-section {
      background: var(--bg2);
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 6rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .policy-inner {
      max-width: 680px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .policy-inner h2 {
      font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.5vw, 2.4rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
    }

    .policy-updated {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      color: var(--dim);
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .policy-block {
      padding-bottom: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .policy-block:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
      padding-bottom: 0;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .policy-block h3 {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--cyan);
      margin-bottom: 0.65rem;
    }

    .policy-block p {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.75;
    }

    .policy-block a { color: var(--cyan2); text-decoration: none; }
    .policy-block a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    /* ─── FOOTER ─── */
    .footer-outer {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    footer {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .footer-logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .footer-logo .logo-dot {
      width: 6px;
      height: 6px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 5px var(--cyan);
    }

    .footer-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1.75rem;
    }

    .footer-links a {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--dim);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.15s;
    }

    .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--text); }

    .footer-copy {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--dim);
    }

    /* ─── RESPONSIVE ─── */
    @media (max-width: 860px) {
      .c2, .c3 { grid-column: span 6; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      nav { padding: 0 1.25rem; }
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .hero { padding: 6rem 1.25rem 5rem; }
      .stats-strip { flex-wrap: wrap; }
      .stat { min-width: 50%; border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
      .footer-links { gap: 1.25rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- ─── NAV ─── -->
  <nav>
    <a href="#" class="logo">
      <span class="logo-dot"></span>
      Spectre
    </a>
    <div class="nav-right">
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="#features">Features</a></li>
        <li><a href="#download">Download</a></li>
        <li><a href="#privacy-policy">Privacy</a></li>
      </ul>
      <a href="https://github.com/koelss/Spectre" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="nav-gh">
        ↗ GitHub
      </a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main>

    <!-- ─── HERO ─── -->
    <section class="hero" id="download">
      <div class="hero-glow"></div>

      <div class="badge">
        <span class="badge-pulse"></span>
        v0.1-alpha — building now
      </div>

      <h1>
        <span class="line-ghost">browse</span>
        <span class="line-solid">without a <span class="accent">trace.</span></span>
      </h1>

      <p class="hero-sub">
        Spectre is a Firefox fork with tracking protection, fingerprint
        resistance, and zero telemetry — compiled in, not just configured.
      </p>

      <div class="download-wrap" id="download-wrap">
        <button id="btn-primary" class="btn-primary soon" onclick="return false;">
          <span id="btn-icon">⬇</span>
          <span id="btn-label">Download Spectre</span>
        </button>
        <div class="platform-row">
          <button class="btn-platform" onclick="return false;">win x64</button>
          <button class="btn-platform" onclick="return false;">linux x64</button>
          <button class="btn-platform" onclick="return false;">macos arm</button>
        </div>
        <span class="platform-hint" id="platform-hint">detecting platform…</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ─── STATS STRIP ─── -->
    <div class="stats-strip">
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat-value g">0</span>
        <span class="stat-label">bytes of data collected</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat-value c">100%</span>
        <span class="stat-label">open source</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat-value">AMO</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Firefox extensions work</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat-value">OFF</span>
        <span class="stat-label">auto-updates disabled</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ─── FEATURES ─── -->
    <section class="section" id="features">
      <span class="section-tag">What's different</span>
      <h2>Privacy on by default.<br />Not as a setting.</h2>

      <div class="bento">

        <!-- row 1: two halves -->
        <div class="card c3">
          <span class="card-icon">🛡</span>
          <div class="card-title">Strict Tracking Protection</div>
          <p class="card-body">
            Blocks trackers, cryptominers, social tracking scripts, and fingerprinters
            the moment you launch — no setup, no toggle required.
          </p>
          <span class="card-chip">on by default</span>
        </div>

        <div class="card c3">
          <span class="card-icon">📡</span>
          <div class="card-title">Zero Telemetry</div>
          <p class="card-body">
            All Mozilla telemetry, crash reporting, and health reports are removed at
            compile time. There's no opt-out because there's nothing to opt out of.
          </p>
          <span class="card-chip">compiled out</span>
        </div>

        <!-- row 2: 2 + 2 + 2 -->
        <div class="card c2">
          <span class="card-icon">🎭</span>
          <div class="card-title">Fingerprint Resistance</div>
          <p class="card-body">
            <code>resistFingerprinting</code> and first-party isolation prevent sites
            from profiling your browser environment.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card c2">
          <span class="card-icon">🔒</span>
          <div class="card-title">HTTPS-Only</div>
          <p class="card-body">
            Every connection is forced to HTTPS. Spectre warns you before falling
            back to an unencrypted connection.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card c2">
          <span class="card-icon">🌐</span>
          <div class="card-title">DNS over HTTPS</div>
          <p class="card-body">
            DNS resolves through an encrypted resolver by default, so your ISP can't
            log every site you visit.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- row 3: 2 + 2 + 2 -->
        <div class="card c2">
          <span class="card-icon">🧩</span>
          <div class="card-title">Firefox Extensions</div>
          <p class="card-body">
            Full AMO compatibility. uBlock Origin, Bitwarden, everything you already
            use — works out of the box.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card c2">
          <span class="card-icon">🚫</span>
          <div class="card-title">No Pocket, No Ads</div>
          <p class="card-body">
            Pocket, sponsored top sites, and all built-in advertising surfaces are
            stripped from the build entirely.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card c2">
          <span class="card-icon">🔗</span>
          <div class="card-title">WebRTC IP Leak Fix</div>
          <p class="card-body">
            WebRTC is restricted to proxy-only mode so your real IP can't be leaked
            by video or voice call sites.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ─── FORK NOTICE ─── -->
    <div class="fork-wrap">
      <div class="fork-inner">
        <span style="font-size:1.3rem;flex-shrink:0">🦊</span>
        <p>
          <strong>Spectre is a fork of Mozilla Firefox.</strong> It inherits full
          compatibility with Firefox extensions (AMO), Mozilla's Gecko rendering
          engine, and the existing Firefox security model — then layers privacy
          defaults on top that Mozilla ships as opt-in. Spectre is not affiliated
          with or endorsed by Mozilla Corporation.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ─── PRIVACY POLICY ─── -->
    <section class="policy-section" id="privacy-policy">
      <div class="policy-inner">
        <span class="section-tag">Legal</span>
        <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
        <span class="policy-updated">Last updated — April 2026</span>

        <div class="policy-block">
          <h3>What Spectre collects</h3>
          <p>
            <strong style="color:var(--green)">Nothing.</strong> Spectre Browser does not collect,
            transmit, or store any data about you or your browsing. Telemetry, crash reporting,
            and health reports are disabled at the build level — there is no opt-out because there
            is nothing to opt out of.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-block">
          <h3>This website</h3>
          <p>
            The Spectre homepage does not use cookies, analytics, or tracking scripts.
            No third-party analytics provider has access to your visit. The only external
            request is to Google Fonts to load the Inter and JetBrains Mono typefaces.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-block">
          <h3>GitHub</h3>
          <p>
            Spectre's source code is hosted on GitHub. Downloading a release means
            connecting to GitHub's servers and CDN, which are subject to
            <a href="https://docs.github.com/en/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-general-privacy-statement"
               target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub's privacy policy</a>.
            Spectre has no control over data GitHub collects during that request.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-block">
          <h3>Firefox upstream</h3>
          <p>
            Spectre is a fork of Mozilla Firefox. While we disable all of Mozilla's data
            collection at build time, the underlying Gecko engine may still make network
            requests for legitimate browser functionality (e.g. Safe Browsing list updates,
            certificate revocation checks). These are not telemetry and are standard browser
            security infrastructure.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-block">
          <h3>Updates</h3>
          <p>
            Spectre's auto-updater is disabled. You will never receive an automatic
            background update. New versions are announced on GitHub Releases, and you choose
            when and whether to upgrade.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-block">
          <h3>Contact</h3>
          <p>
            Questions or concerns? Open an issue on
            <a href="https://github.com/koelss/Spectre/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>

  <!-- ─── FOOTER ─── -->
